videos.description: Jermaine Couisnard inbounds a pass to James Reese at half court, and Reese buries a 3-pointer as time expires to give South Carolina a 77-74 win over Ole Miss.
videos.headline: 'A South Carolina shocker!' James' Reese's half-court 3 wins it in OT
